sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Gateway
    participant Middleware as Auth Middleware
    participant AuthService as Auth Service (NATS)
    participant Handler as Protected Handler

    Note over Client,Handler: Запрос к защищенному эндпоинту

    Client->>Gateway: GET /api/v1/users<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}<br/>Cookie: fingerprint={fp}

    Gateway->>Middleware: Process Request

    Middleware->>Middleware: Extract token from<br/>Authorization header

    alt Missing Authorization header
        Middleware-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized<br/>"Authorization header required"
    end

    Middleware->>Middleware: Extract fingerprint<br/>from cookie

    alt Missing fingerprint cookie
        Middleware-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized<br/>"Authentication fingerprint missing"
    end

    Middleware->>AuthService: NATS Request: auth.validate<br/>{token, fingerprint}

    AuthService->>AuthService: Validate token<br/>Check signature<br/>Check expiration<br/>Check fingerprint match<br/>Check blacklist

    alt Token invalid or expired
        AuthService-->>Middleware: {success: true, data: {valid: false}}
        Middleware-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized<br/>"Invalid or expired token"
    end

    alt Fingerprint mismatch
        AuthService-->>Middleware: {success: true, data: {valid: false}}
        Middleware-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized<br/>"Invalid or expired token"
    end

    AuthService-->>Middleware: {success: true,<br/>data: {valid: true, user_id, role, jti}}

    Middleware->>Middleware: Store AuthUser in context<br/>{ID, Role, JTI}

    Middleware->>Handler: Next() - Pass to handler

    Handler->>Handler: Get AuthUser from context<br/>Process business logic

    Handler-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>Response data

    Note over Client,Handler: Пользователь успешно авторизован
